        "setup": "In [Google Cloud Console](https://console.cloud.google.com/), select or create a project, enable the [Chrome Management API](https://developers.google.com/chrome/management/guides/setup), then create a service account in [IAM & Admin > Service Accounts](https://console.cloud.google.com/iam-admin/serviceaccounts). For customer data access, the setup guide says service-account apps may require domain-wide delegation to a Google Workspace admin account; see the Chrome Management [Initial Setup guide](https://developers.google.com/chrome/management/guides/setup). Use the service account to mint Google OAuth access tokens for this API.",
